  "content": "\n \n \n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"248\" data-backw=\"578\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"505088743\" data-ratio=\"0.4287037037037037\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f8a97cde-c5a5-4872-d243-24bcb6c68500/public\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f8a97cde-c5a5-4872-d243-24bcb6c68500/public\">\n  </section>\n  <h3 style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <section data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n      <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n       <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin: -1.2em 8px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\"></p>\n        <p style=\"margin: -1.2em 8px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-family: inherit;font-size: 1em;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:inherit;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:inherit;\">新智元报道&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section></h3>\n  <section style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\">编辑：LRST</span>\n  </section>\n  <section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n     <h5 style=\"padding:10px;margin:10px 8px 0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;max-width:100%;word-break:break-all !important;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">【新智元导读】</strong>OmniParser V2可将屏幕截图转换为结构化元素，帮助LLM理解和操作GUI；在检测小图标和推理速度上显著提升，延迟降低60%，与多种LLM结合后表现优异。</span></h5>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">图形用户界面（GUI）自动化需要智能体具备理解和交互用户屏幕的能力。</span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">然而，使用通用大型语言模型（LLM）作为GUI智能体仍然存在难点：1）如何可靠地识别用户界面中的可交互图标，以及 2）理解截图中各种元素的语义，并准确地将预期的操作与屏幕上的相应区域关联起来。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">OmniParser通过将UI截图从像素空间「token化」为LLM可解释的结构化元素，弥合了这一差距，使得LLM能够在一组已解析的可交互元素基础上进行基于检索的下一步动作预测。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"241\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"658\" data-imgfileid=\"505088005\" data-ratio=\"0.42962962962962964\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0f06837d-1414-4164-1e29-17bc81fe7e00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1530\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0f06837d-1414-4164-1e29-17bc81fe7e00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">代码: https://github.com/microsoft/OmniParser/tree/master</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">模型: https://huggingface.co/microsoft/OmniParser-v2.0</span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Demo：https://huggingface.co/spaces/microsoft/OmniParser-v2</span></p>\n  <section autoid=\"1895\" data-style-type=\"0\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-bottom:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p>OmniParser方法概述</p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">可交互区域检测</span></strong></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">从UI屏幕中识别可交互区域是推理用户任务应执行何种操作的关键步骤。与其直接让GPT-4o预测屏幕上应操作的xy坐标，研究人员采用Set-of-Marks，在UI截图上叠加可交互图标的边界框，并让GPT-4V生成要操作的边界框ID。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">具体而言，研究人员构建了一个独特UI截图的可交互图标检测数据集，每张图片都标注了从DOM tree提取的可交互图标的边界框。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">数据采集时，首先从Bing Index热门网址中随机抽取100,000个URL，并从其DOM中提取网页的可交互区域边界框。部分网页及其可交互区域示例如图2所示。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-size: 16px;\">融合功能性icon semantics</span></strong>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">研究人员发现，仅输入带有边界框和对应ID的UI截图，往往会导致GPT-4o产生误导性预测，这一局限性可能源于GPT-4o在同时执行两个任务时的能力受限：一是识别每个图标的语义信息，二是预测特定图标的下一步操作。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为了解决这一问题，研究人员在提示（prompt）中加入功能的局部语义信息。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">具体而言，对于可交互区域检测模型识别出的每个图标，使用一个微调模型生成该图标的功能描述。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">通过构建专门的图标描述数据集，研究人员发现该模型在常见应用图标的描述上更加可靠；在UI截图的视觉提示基础上，加入局部边界框的语义信息（以文本提示的形式）能够显著提升GPT-4o的理解效果。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section autoid=\"1895\" data-style-type=\"0\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-bottom:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p>构建专用数据集<span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"></span></p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"720\" data-imgfileid=\"505088007\" data-ratio=\"0.6863679694947569\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4d8c71e0-5529-42da-d55f-3cc225693a00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1049\" data-width=\"1049\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4d8c71e0-5529-42da-d55f-3cc225693a00/public\"></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">OmniParser的开发始于两个核心数据集的构建：</span>\n  </section>\n  <ul start=\"1\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">可交互图标检测数据集：</span></strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">该数据集来源于Bing Index热门网页，并经过自动化标注以突出可点击和可操作区域。</span></span>\n    </section></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">图标描述数据集：</span></strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">该数据集为每个UI元素关联其功能描述，是训练模型理解检测元素语义的关键</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">数据。研究人员收集了苹果App store和windows app store每个app类别前十名的app icon logo，和一系列常用software界面的icons的image/caption pair作为训练数据</span></p></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 0px;\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">OmniParser V1实验结果</span></strong></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">通过这些解析结果，OmniParser显著提升了GPT-4V在多个基准测试（ScreenSpot、Mind2Web、AITW、WindowsAgentArena）上的表现：</span>\n  </section>\n  <ul start=\"1\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">Mind2Web：</span></strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">OmniParser+GPT-4V的表现优于使用HTML额外信息的GPT-4V代理。</span></span>\n    </section></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">AITW：</span></strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">OmniParser超越了结合Android图标检测模型（使用视图层级训练）的GPT-4V。</span></span>\n    </section></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">WindowsAgentArena：</span></strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">OmniParser在该全新基准测试上取得S</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">OTA成绩</span>\n    </section></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Multimodal Mind2Web</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"137\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"312\" data-imgfileid=\"505088009\" data-ratio=\"0.24351851851851852\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ac9ecdd0-393e-440c-08fb-785e97595a00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1280\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ac9ecdd0-393e-440c-08fb-785e97595a00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AITW</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"84\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"192\" data-imgfileid=\"505088004\" data-ratio=\"0.15\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a66c32d4-4ff6-42cb-5996-7176aed09600/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1280\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a66c32d4-4ff6-42cb-5996-7176aed09600/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Windows agent arena</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"132\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"301\" data-imgfileid=\"505088006\" data-ratio=\"0.2351851851851852\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2d4f6c06-2612-4fb4-ebdb-f0ea0c2b9400/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1280\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2d4f6c06-2612-4fb4-ebdb-f0ea0c2b9400/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 0px;\">\n   <strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">OmniParser V2带来哪些新东西？</span></strong>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">OmniParser V2将屏幕理解能力提升到了新的水平。与V1相比，它在检测更小的可交互元素方面达到了更高的准确率，同时推理速度更快，使其成为GUI自动化的有力工具。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">具体而言，OmniParser V2采用了更大规模的交互元素检测数据和图标功能描述数据进行训练。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">此外，通过减少图标描述模型的图像输入尺寸，OmniParser V2的推理延迟比上一版本降低了60%</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">值得注意的是，OmniParser与GPT-4o结合后，在最新发布的 ScreenSpot Pro基准测试上达到了39.6%的平均准确率，该基准测试具有高分辨率屏幕和极小的目标图标，相比GPT-4o原始得分0.8有了显著提升。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为了加快不同智能体设置的实验速度，研究人员创建了OmniTool，一个Docker化的Windows系统，集成了一套代理所需的重要工具。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">OmniTool开箱即用地支持OmniParser与多种最先进的LLM结合使用，包括OpenAI（4o/o1/o3-mini）、DeepSeek（R1）、Qwen（2.5VL）和Anthropic（Sonnet），从而实现屏幕理解、目标对齐、行动规划和执行等功能。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><iframe class=\"video_iframe rich_pages\" data-vidtype=\"2\" data-mpvid=\"wxv_3886953247369592837\" data-cover=\"http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3ybxwVFyPXoKK1MtMsDFBTtw5UYyfgMFiakw0RHP82bub2OULdxIicvA9NHTboX09rIQrJ2eqUDeSg%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" data-ratio=\"1.7647058823529411\" data-w=\"960\" data-src=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_3886953247369592837\"></iframe></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 0px;\">\n   <strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">风险与缓解措施</span></strong>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为了符合「微软AI原则」和「负责任AI实践」，研究人员通过使用负责任AI数据训练图标描述模型来进行风险缓解，有助于模型尽可能避免推测出现在图标图像中的个人的敏感属性（如种族、宗教等）。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">同时，研究人员鼓励用户仅在不包含有害内容的截图上使用OmniParser，最好在使用过程中保持人工审核，以尽量降低风险。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">针对OmniTool，研究人员使用「微软威胁建模工具」进行威胁模型分析，并在GitHub仓库中提供了沙盒Docker容器、安全指南和示例。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\">参考资料：</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: left;\">https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/articl</span><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: left;\">es/omniparser-v2-turning-any-llm-into-a-computer-use-agent/</span></span></section>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "微软开源 OmniParser V2，通过结构化 UI 元素显著提升大语言模型在 GUI 自动化中的性能和效率，并降低推理延迟达 60%。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "微软开源 OmniParser V2，通过结构化 UI 元素显著提升大语言模型在 GUI 自动化中的性能和效率，并降低推理延迟达 60%。",
  "summary": "文章介绍了微软开源的 OmniParser V2，旨在解决通用大语言模型（LLM）在图形用户界面（GUI）自动化中面临的挑战，如识别可交互图标和理解界面元素语义。OmniParser V2 通过将 UI 截图转换为 LLM 可解释的结构化元素，弥合了像素空间和语义理解之间的差距。该版本在检测小图标和推理速度上显著提升，延迟降低 60%。OmniParser V2 还与 GPT-4o 等多种 LLM 结合，在 ScreenSpot Pro 等基准测试中表现出色，尤其是在高分辨率屏幕和极小目标图标的 ScreenSpot Pro 基准测试中，准确率提升显著。为了方便实验，微软还提供了 OmniTool，一个集成了必要工具的 Docker 化 Windows 系统。文章还提到了微软在 AI 伦理和安全方面的考虑，以及相应的风险缓解措施。",
